odb is an Object DataBase

Which means a database for storing objects in the sense of 'real world' objects

odb ist intended to save information as real world visitors would register them

  - sequencially
  - spontan
  - without any plan
  - ad hoc
  - not knowing what it is
  - as time allows it
  - as detailed as necessary
  - ...

object by object, atom by atom, relation by relation, filling up meadows,
linked onto strings, ...
